{"id":328963,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/01/global-voices-缅甸：十张老照片-带你回到1897/","date":"2014-01-09T16:00:44Z","modified":"2014-01-09T16:00:44Z","title":"Global Voices | 缅甸：十张老照片 带你回到1897","content":"<p><p>大英图书馆在<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/\">Flickr</a>相簿上，向大众公开丰富的收藏，藏品主要是来自世界上许多国家的历史照片、地图与其他插图。我们发现两本1897年出版的书籍，里头有缅甸旅游的旧照片。透过这些照片，我们可一窥19世纪晚期缅甸社会的生活样貌。</p>\n<p>以下五张照片选自《漫游缅甸（Wanderings in Burma）》这本书，作者是George W Bird：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11240238705/sizes/l/\"><img alt=\"Alguada Lighthouse\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/burma-lighthouse.jpg\" width=\"530\" height=\"800\"></a></p>\n<p>Alguada灯塔</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11241295674/sizes/c/\"><img alt=\"Sagaing Hills\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/sagaing-hills.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"530\"></a></p>\n<p>实皆山</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11241598375/sizes/c/\"><img alt=\"A steamer at Irrawaddy River\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/flotilla.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"537\"></a></p>\n<p>伊洛瓦底江畔的汽船</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11243436484/sizes/l/\"><img alt=\"Cargo steamers\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/cargo.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"720\"></a></p>\n<p>蒸汽货轮</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11241086726/sizes/c/\"><img alt=\"A pagoda in Rangoon\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/burma-pagoda.jpg\" width=\"541\" height=\"800\"></a></p>\n<p>仰光的宝塔</p>\n</div>\n<p>Alice Hart也在1897年出版了《风景如画的缅甸（Picturesque Burma）》这本书。以下是几张书中的照片：</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11240952403/sizes/c/\"><img alt=\"burma carriage\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/burma-carriage.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"642\"></a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11243161503/sizes/c/\"><img alt=\"Taming a wild elephant\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/elephant.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"561\"></a></p>\n<p>驯服野生大象</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11297381656/sizes/c/\"><img alt=\"Net fishing\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/net-fishing.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"683\"></a></p>\n<p>撒网捕鱼</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11297397064/sizes/c/\"><img alt=\"Bamboo houses\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/bamboo-houses.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"498\"></a></p>\n<p>竹屋</p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/britishlibrary/11239979815/sizes/c/\"><img alt=\"burma women\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/burma-women.jpg\" width=\"593\" height=\"800\"></a></p>\n<div>校对：Fen</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2014/01/02/10-vintage-photos-of-burma-in-1897/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://zh.gl